Subject: report for unresolved SIDs in AD groups
Description: Does SA active directory module have an out of the box method or something to discover unresolved sids that is on an AD group? see screenshots for some details
Solution_Comment__c:
https://netwrix.productboard.com/all-notes/notes/40625991

Workaround:  I was able to connect the GroupMembersView ADI table with the Users table and pull in the “isdeleted” attribute to identify which users that still belong to AD groups but their actual AD account no longer exists.
